 * LCD SCL          A5    (SCL)
 * RTC GND          GND
 * RTC VCC          5V
 * RTC SDA          A4    (SDA)
 * RTC SCL          A5    (SCL)
 * Radio GND        GND
 * Radio VCC        3,3V  (!!!) 
